{
  "texts": [
    "Addressing these limitations in future research could improve the accessibility, generalizability, and ethical applicability of LLM-based psychological assessment tools.",
    "Reddit SuicideWatch and Mental Health Collection (SWMH) The SWMH (Ji et al., 2021)",
    "dataset contains 54,412 Reddit posts that discuss various mental health conditions.",
    "Each post is labeled with one of the following categories: depression, anxiety, bipolar disorder, or suicidal ideation.",
    "The dataset is divided by the authors that published it as follows: training set: 34,824 samples (64%); validation set: 8,706 samples (16%); test set: 10,882 samples (20%)."
  ]
}